@startuml 哪吒网络安全-程序启动序列
' =============================================================================
' 哪吒网络安全 TUI —— 程序启动序列图
' 描述: 从用户执行命令到进入事件循环主循环的完整启动流程
' =============================================================================

title 哪吒网络安全 —— 程序启动序列图

skinparam backgroundColor #121218
skinparam defaultFontColor #DCDCE6
skinparam sequenceArrowColor #00D4FF
skinparam participantBackgroundColor #1E1E2E
skinparam participantBorderColor #32324B
skinparam noteBackgroundColor #1A1A2E
skinparam noteBorderColor #00D4FF
skinparam lifeLineColor #32324B

actor "用户" as User
participant "main()\n入口函数" as Main
participant "env\n环境变量" as EnvLoader
participant "文件系统\nYAML 解析" as FS
participant "终端\ncrossterm" as Terminal
participant "tokio\n异步运行时" as Tokio
participant "App\n全局状态" as App

== 阶段一: 环境初始化 ==

User -> Main : 执行 ./nezha_cyber
activate Main

Main -> Main : dotenvy::dotenv()
Main -> EnvLoader : 读取 .env 文件
activate EnvLoader
EnvLoader --> Main : DEEPSEEK_TOKEN / DEEPSEEK_API_KEY
deactivate EnvLoader

== 阶段二: 配置加载 ==

Main -> FS : load_agents()
activate FS
FS -> FS : 检查 agents.yaml 是否存在？
alt agents.yaml 存在且格式正确
    FS -> FS : serde_yaml::from_str()
    FS --> Main : Vec<AgentConfig> (自定义配置)
else agents.yaml 不存在或解析失败
    FS --> Main : default_agents() (3 个内置智能体)
end
deactivate FS

Main -> FS : load_app_config()
activate FS
FS -> FS : 检查 config.yaml 是否存在？
alt config.yaml 存在
    FS --> Main : AppConfig (YAML 配置)
else 无 config.yaml
    FS --> Main : AppConfig::default()
end
deactivate FS

note right of Main
  AppConfig 包含:
  - api_base (默认 api.deepseek.com)
  - api_key (从环境变量)
  - default_model (deepseek-chat)
  - default_pricing (2.0/8.0)
end note

== 阶段三: 终端接管 ==

Main -> Terminal : enable_raw_mode()
activate Terminal
Terminal --> Main : raw mode 已启用
Main -> Terminal : EnterAlternateScreen
Main -> Terminal : EnableMouseCapture
Main -> Terminal : 清屏
deactivate Terminal

note right of Main
  终端进入全屏模式:
  - 原始输入 (无行缓冲)
  - 交替屏幕 (独立缓冲区)
  - 鼠标事件捕获
end note

== 阶段四: 运行时与状态初始化 ==

Main -> Tokio : Runtime::new()
activate Tokio

Main -> Tokio : mpsc::unbounded_channel<Action>()
Tokio --> Main : (tx, rx) 通道对

Main -> App : App::new(agents, app_config)
activate App
App -> App : 创建 DeepSeekClient\n(api_base, api_key, model)
App -> App : 创建默认标签页 Tab(0,"会话 1")
App -> App : 设置默认主题 "cyber-dark"
App --> Main : App 初始状态
deactivate App

== 阶段五: 进入事件循环 ==

Main -> Tokio : rt.block_on(async { loop })

note over Main, Tokio
  ====== 事件循环已启动 ======
  1. terminal.draw() 渲染 UI
  2. event::poll() 等待输入
  3. update() 处理状态变更
  4. 回到步骤 1

  退出条件: app.should_quit == true
end note

Main -> Tokio : 事件循环运行中...
deactivate Main

== 阶段六: 正常退出 ==

User -> Main : 按 Ctrl+C
activate Main
Main -> Main : Action::Shutdown\n-> app.should_quit = true
Main -> Terminal : cleanup_terminal()
activate Terminal
Terminal -> Terminal : disable_raw_mode()
Terminal -> Terminal : DisableMouseCapture
Terminal -> Terminal : LeaveAlternateScreen
deactivate Terminal
Main -> User : 终端恢复，程序退出
deactivate Main
deactivate Tokio

center footer 哪吒网络安全 TUI · 启动序列 · 共计 6 个阶段
@enduml
